{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "AOM or OOM that triggers when talking to Elminster.Elminster does a brief introduction before joining the camp, potentially taking the players along.Can trigger in either Creche or SCL.",
    "how_to_trigger": "- Give Gale at least one magic item, go to SCL_Main_A, and, without the Avatar, approach Elminster at S_ORI_Gale_ElminsterPoint_SCL_975ef355-b68e-4061-bda8-b774e8ff552fOR- Give Gale at least one magic item, without the Avatar, go to CRE_Main_A, and approach Elminster at S_ORI_Gale_ElminsterPoint_CRE_f5a225ef-d123-449f-98e2-53309a21979b"
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "24": {
      "id": "24",
      "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
      "text": "Ho there, wanderer. Stay thy course a moment to indulge an old man.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "AOM"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "17",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "23": {
          "id": "23",
          "speaker": "Gale",
          "text": "Elminster?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "17",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "5": {
              "id": "5",
              "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
              "text": "The very same, Gale. And a fair bit miffed he is, too, finding himself forced to expose his best pair of boots to so many miles of country road on your behalf.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "17",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "15": {
                  "id": "15",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "My sympathies for your wearied soles. Care to explain what you're doing?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "17",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "20": {
                      "id": "20",
                      "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                      "text": "I was bid to spare neither time nor my own self to find you. She sent me, Gale. You know of whom I speak.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "17",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "8": {
                          "id": "8",
                          "speaker": "Gale",
                          "text": "Mystra? What does she want of me?",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "17",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "9": {
                              "id": "9",
                              "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                              "text": "Mystra, aye, m'boy. But what she wants is a matter better discussed in more comfortable environs. Knowing you, I'll wager your camp is a veritable home away from home.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "17": {
                                  "id": "17",
                                  "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                                  "text": "Lead the way - then I can rest these bones of mine for a spell, and you can learn all I have to share.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "18": {
                                      "id": "18",
                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                      "text": "All right, let's go.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "0": {
                                          "id": "0",
                                          "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                                          "text": "Marvellous. Onward, then.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [
                                            "ORI_Gale_Event_PlayersWithElminsterToCamp",
                                            "ORI_Gale_Event_ElminsterToCamp"
                                          ],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    },
                                    "28": {
                                      "id": "28",
                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                      "text": "Head to my camp yourself. I'll join when I can.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "11": {
                                          "id": "11",
                                          "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                                          "text": "Perhaps I didn't convey the gravity of the situation, if you think you have better things to be doing. But very well, I shall see you there.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [
                                            "ORI_Gale_Event_ElminsterToCamp"
                                          ],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "33": {
                          "id": "33",
                          "speaker": "Gale",
                          "text": "Don't keep me in suspense, Elminster.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "17",
